00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:22,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Best of luck to you and your baby!</font>

177
00:10:23,350 --> 00:10:25,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got this!</font>

178
00:10:28,270 --> 00:10:30,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh no!</i></font>

179
00:10:30,770 --> 00:10:32,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What am I doing?!</font>

180
00:10:32,530 --> 00:10:34,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-There's only seven minutes left!</font>

181
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:37,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe I can catch the same taxi...</font>

182
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't have enough money!</font>

183
00:10:39,500 --> 00:10:41,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shoot!</font>

184
00:10:41,130 --> 00:10:43,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What if I walk back?</font>

185
00:10:44,900 --> 00:10:47,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-It'll take thirty minutes...</font>

186
00:10:48,430 --> 00:10:51,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Still... I can probably make it 
in time for the finale!</i></font>

187
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:10,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to watch the fireworks 
with just you, Eiyu!</i></font>

188
00:11:18,740 --> 00:11:21,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello? Eiyu?</font>

189
00:11:22,200 --> 00:11:24,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... Sorry.</font>

190
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:27,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wait, what? It's hard to hear...</i></font>

191
00:11:27,870 --> 00:11:30,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't make it to the fireworks show.</font>

192
00:11:30,970 --> 00:11:32,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So sorry!</font>

193
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:34,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something came up all of a sudden.</font>

194
00:11:34,780 --> 00:11:38,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Enjoy the fireworks with Akarin... okay?</font>

195
00:11:40,020 --> 00:11:42,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously, don't worry about me.</font>

196
00:11:42,440 --> 00:11:44,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Talk to you later!</font>

197
00:11:47,690 --> 00:11:50,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With Akarin... huh?</font>

198
00:11:51,390 --> 00:11:53,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What else could I have said?</i></font>

199
00:11:53,770 --> 00:11:57,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's no way I could've 
told him the truth.</i></font>

200
00:11:59,020 --> 00:12:00,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yonosuke-kun.</font>

201
00:12:00,280 --> 00:12:02,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take good care of Shio, okay?</font>

202
00:12:03,960 --> 00:12:05,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dad!</font>

203
00:12:07,290 --> 00:12:09,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See you later, Dad!</font>

204
00:12:14,980 --> 00:12:16,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Take that! Take that!</i></font>

205
00:12:16,940 --> 00:12:17,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>All right!</i></font>

206
00:12:17,590 --> 00:12:18,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yonosuke-kun.</font>

207
00:12:18,870 --> 00:12:20,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's late now.</font>

208
00:12:20,490 --> 00:12:23,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should probably go home 
before you get scolded!</font>

209
00:12:23,610 --> 00:12:25,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your mom's still at work, right?</font>

210
00:12:25,810 --> 00:12:26,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

211
00:12:27,130 --> 00:12:28,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be here until she comes back.</font>

212
00:12:29,690 --> 00:12:30,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

213
00:12:30,900 --> 00:12:32,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't leave you by yourself.</font>

214
00:12:36,630 --> 00:12:37,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

215
00:12:37,680 --> 00:12:39,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right!</font>

216
00:12:39,650 --> 00:12:41,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Player 2, you win!</i></font>

217
00:12:42,110 --> 00:12:43,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won!</font>

218
00:12:43,510 --> 00:12:46,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! You just want to play the game!</font>

219
00:12:46,330 --> 00:12:48,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Come on, let's play another round!</i></font>

220
00:12:49,290 --> 00:12:50,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yeah, there's no way I can tell him.</i></font>

221
00:12:51,180 --> 00:12:54,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He'd rush over, worried sick.</i></font>

222
00:12:55,870 --> 00:12:59,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Akarin and I finally 
mustered up the courage to ask.</i></font>

223
00:12:59,910 --> 00:13:02,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So I don't want to mess things up.</i></font>

224
00:13:10,210 --> 00:13:12,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It started...</font>

225
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:17,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The couple who kiss during the final, 
massive fireworks...</font>

226
00:13:18,830 --> 00:13:21,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...are destined to be together.</font>

227
00:13:28,540 --> 00:13:30,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eiyu...?</font>

228
00:13:32,330 --> 00:13:34,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, excuse me.</font>

229
00:13:34,030 --> 00:13:35,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you the one who helped 
my wife at the festival?</font>

230
00:13:35,870 --> 00:13:37,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yes.</font>

231
00:13:37,800 --> 00:13:40,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew it was you! Thank you very much.</font>

232
00:13:40,620 --> 00:13:42,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really can't thank you 
enough for your help!</font>

233
00:13:42,330 --> 00:13:43,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, please... I was happy to help.</font>

234
00:13:43,950 --> 00:13:46,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But... is everything okay?</font>

235
00:13:46,230 --> 00:13:47,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

236
00:13:47,970 --> 00:13:50,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't you have plans with someone?</font>

237
00:13:51,240 --> 00:13:53,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Plans...</i></font>

238
00:13:56,680 --> 00:13:58,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No hard feelings to each other, okay?</font>

239
00:13:59,200 --> 00:14:02,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Meet me at the torii gate at eight.</font>

240
00:14:05,790 --> 00:14:06,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me.</font>

241
00:14:06,780 --> 00:14:07,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

242
00:14:08,510 --> 00:14:10,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is something the matter?</font>

243
00:14:10,110 --> 00:14:11,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

244
00:14:12,660 --> 00:14:14,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's nothing, really.</font>

245
00:14:14,700 --> 00:14:16,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't have just left her.</font>

246
00:14:17,210 --> 00:14:21,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm sure Eiyu would've done the same.</i></font>

247
00:14:24,870 --> 00:14:26,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"I can't leave you by yourself."</i></font>

248
00:14:27,600 --> 00:14:28,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's right!</i></font>

249
00:14:29,720 --> 00:14:31,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Eiyu was always generous.</i></font>

250
00:14:32,730 --> 00:14:35,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're ever feeling lonely, 
just let me know.</font>

251
00:14:36,990 --> 00:14:40,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Eiyu was always there to support me.</i></font>

252
00:14:41,860 --> 00:14:46,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know you were getting even 
more nauseous than me, you dummy.</font>

253
00:14:47,160 --> 00:14:50,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In my heart... it's always been Eiyu!</i></font>

254
00:14:51,210 --> 00:14:53,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sorry... Akarin!</i></font>

255
00:14:55,490 --> 00:14:57,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew it!</font>

256
00:14:57,630 --> 00:14:59,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have been friends since childhood.</font>

257
00:15:00,600 --> 00:15:03,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to watch 
the fireworks with Eiyu, too!</i></font>

258
00:15:09,650 --> 00:15:11,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And be with him during 
the final, massive fireworks!</i></font>

259
00:15:23,520 --> 00:15:28,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This concludes tonight's fireworks show.</i></font>

260
00:15:28,840 --> 00:15:30,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's over...</font>

261
00:15:30,600 --> 00:15:34,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The fireworks... ended...</font>

262
00:15:37,090 --> 00:15:39,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eiyu... The truth is...</font>

263
00:15:39,930 --> 00:15:43,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I... I wanted to watch them with you...</font>

264
00:15:44,520 --> 00:15:47,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The fireworks... together...</font>

265
00:15:47,250 --> 00:15:50,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then you should've said so
in the first place.</font>

266
00:15:57,360 --> 00:15:58,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">E-Eiyu?!</font>

267
00:15:58,620 --> 00:16:00,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing here?</font>

268
00:16:00,110 --> 00:16:01,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's Akarin?</font>

269
00:16:01,800 --> 00:16:04,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't you watch the fireworks with her?</font>

270
00:16:05,030 --> 00:16:06,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Akari's...</font>

271
00:16:07,120 --> 00:16:08,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">behind you.</font>

272
00:16:08,530 --> 00:16:09,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You dummy!</font>

273
00:16:11,590 --> 00:16:13,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? But why?!</font>

274
00:16:13,190 --> 00:16:14,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean?!</font>

275
00:16:14,750 --> 00:16:16,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was with that call?!</font>

276
00:16:16,520 --> 00:16:18,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How could we even
enjoy the fireworks</font>

277
00:16:18,420 --> 00:16:20,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">knowing there's something 
going on with you?!</font>

278
00:16:20,050 --> 00:16:21,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

279
00:16:21,850 --> 00:16:22,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't hold it in.</font>

280
00:16:22,990 --> 00:16:26,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you need help, then say so, you dummy!</font>

281
00:16:26,460 --> 00:16:28,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh my gosh, you're barefoot!</font>

282
00:16:28,450 --> 00:16:30,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, you're all scraped up! Are you okay?</font>

283
00:16:33,260 --> 00:16:34,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shio?</font>

284
00:16:35,290 --> 00:16:38,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry... both of you...</font>

285
00:16:39,010 --> 00:16:41,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I ruined the fireworks...</font>

286
00:16:43,170 --> 00:16:44,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's still time.</font>

287
00:16:45,660 --> 00:16:46,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go!</font>

288
00:16:47,280 --> 00:16:48,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

289
00:16:48,930 --> 00:16:50,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's try this again!</font>

290
00:16:50,490 --> 00:16:51,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fireworks time!</font>

291
00:16:57,830 --> 00:16:59,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't this a little wasteful?</font>

292
00:16:59,990 --> 00:17:03,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We never get to do this.
We might as well go all out!</font>

293
00:17:10,960 --> 00:17:11,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

294
00:17:12,240 --> 00:17:15,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How did you know where I was?</font>

295
00:17:15,430 --> 00:17:19,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, about that. Listen to this!</font>

296
00:17:20,040 --> 00:17:21,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Talk to you later!</i></font>

297
00:17:21,460 --> 00:17:22,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Shio!</font>

298
00:17:22,880 --> 00:17:24,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She hung up on me.</font>

299
00:17:26,040 --> 00:17:27,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go, Akari!</font>

300
00:17:27,620 --> 00:17:28,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

301
00:17:28,810 --> 00:17:31,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay...?</font>

302
00:17:31,070 --> 00:17:32,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, Eiyu!</font>

303
00:17:32,320 --> 00:17:33,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where are you going?!</font>

304
00:17:36,770 --> 00:17:38,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-Where should we go?</font>

305
00:17:38,260 --> 00:17:39,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously?</font>

306
00:17:39,330 --> 00:17:40,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's just go!</font>

307
00:17:40,690 --> 00:17:42,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, wait!</font>

308
00:17:43,330 --> 00:17:45,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eiyu was so flustered.</font>

309
00:17:46,120 --> 00:17:47,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sh-Shut up!</font>

310
00:17:48,290 --> 00:17:51,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And when we were looking 
around at the festival...</font>

311
00:17:51,340 --> 00:17:53,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shio! Where are you?</font>

312
00:17:53,750 --> 00:17:55,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shio!</font>

313
00:17:55,350 --> 00:17:57,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shio!</font>

314
00:17:57,130 --> 00:17:58,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shio!</font>

315
00:17:59,180 --> 00:18:01,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me, young lady.</font>

316
00:18:02,100 --> 00:18:04,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you that girl's friend?</font>

317
00:18:04,130 --> 00:18:05,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

318
00:18:05,270 --> 00:18:06,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must be.</font>

319
00:18:06,230 --> 00:18:08,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She was wearing that same hairpin.</font>

320
00:18:10,410 --> 00:18:12,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The elderly woman told us 
everything she saw.</font>

321
00:18:13,560 --> 00:18:15,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She was really grateful for your help.</font>

322
00:18:16,740 --> 00:18:20,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But seriously, ditching 
a date to help someone?</font>

323
00:18:20,130 --> 00:18:23,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're such a Shio, Shio.</font>

324
00:18:26,740 --> 00:18:28,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, well...</font>

325
00:18:29,030 --> 00:18:34,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all good. We can always catch 
the big fireworks next year, right?</font>

326
00:18:34,790 --> 00:18:38,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So for now, let's put 
on our own big show!</font>

327
00:18:39,500 --> 00:18:43,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This fireworks show is for us, 
childhood friends!</font>

328
00:18:45,480 --> 00:18:46,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

329
00:18:49,770 --> 00:18:51,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, let's do this!</font>

330
00:19:01,330 --> 00:19:04,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our fireworks are tiny.</font>

331
00:19:05,230 --> 00:19:07,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why we should've 
launched them all at once!</font>

332
00:19:07,720 --> 00:19:10,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like I said, it's a waste!</font>

333
00:19:10,210 --> 00:19:11,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But, come on!</font>

334
00:19:11,680 --> 00:19:14,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, both of you.</font>

335
00:19:14,940 --> 00:19:18,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This turned out to be the best summer!</font>

336
00:19:27,290 --> 00:19:29,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry, Akarin.</font>

337
00:19:29,610 --> 00:19:31,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I ruined everything.</font>

338
00:19:33,080 --> 00:19:37,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After we finally mustered up 
the courage to ask Eiyu out...</font>

339
00:19:37,200 --> 00:19:38,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

340
00:19:38,320 --> 00:19:40,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you worrying so much about me?</font>

341
00:19:41,500 --> 00:19:43,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean...</font>

342
00:19:43,260 --> 00:19:46,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was the one who initiated all of this...</font>

343
00:19:46,240 --> 00:19:49,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you're an important 
childhood friend, Akarin.</font>

344
00:19:50,020 --> 00:19:51,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really are a dummy!</font>

345
00:19:51,430 --> 00:19:52,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

346
00:19:52,840 --> 00:19:58,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the one who said you wanted to 
be honest and have no hard feelings.</font>

347
00:19:59,150 --> 00:20:01,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When you say, "no hard feelings,"</font>

348
00:20:01,640 --> 00:20:04,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">do you mean a romance 
where you're constantly on edge</font>

349
00:20:04,330 --> 00:20:05,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">with other people's feelings?</font>

350
00:20:08,320 --> 00:20:12,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't need you to do that. 
I'm not that weak anymore.</font>

351
00:20:13,850 --> 00:20:16,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't let it happen like this.</font>

352
00:20:16,610 --> 00:20:19,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll win fair and square!</font>

353
00:20:29,310 --> 00:20:30,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Understood.</font>

354
00:20:39,610 --> 00:20:41,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He fell asleep.</font>

355
00:20:41,080 --> 00:20:42,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look at that dumb face.</font>

356
00:20:42,890 --> 00:20:45,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's always been like this.</font>

357
00:20:45,390 --> 00:20:47,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He wore himself out from 
all the excitement earlier.</font>

358
00:20:47,770 --> 00:20:50,400
